<br>
The staff you receive from getting the powder from Tolapumj is not recommended to be used for the epic.<br>
<br>
For starter's if you read the quest walkthrough, your missing a major component which is the green oil which makes Kandin give you a note (which is critical) and the staff. The note is used to spawn the final turn in mob in Halas.<br>
<br>
If you don't have the note from doing the broken golem it looks like nothing will work and you will lose all your staffs during final turn in. GM's wont help you either.<br>
<br>
I have an extra mistletoe powder in the bank I got from my last juggs raid and am planning to use it one day for an extra staff.<br>
